article.description: — Chase Johnston had a career-high 24 points as Stetson topped Jacksonville 91-75 on Friday night.
article.headline: Johnston scores 24 to carry Stetson past Jacksonville 91-75
article.linkText: Johnston scores 24 to carry Stetson past Jacksonville 91-75
article.story: DELAND, Fla. -- — Chase Johnston had a career-high 24 points as Stetson topped Jacksonville 91-75 on Friday night. Rob Perry had 18 points for Stetson (9-11, 6-7 Atlantic Sun Conference). Christiaan Jones added 15 points. Mahamadou Diawara had 13 points. Kevion Nolan had 17 points for the Dolphins (10-13, 4-9). Tyreese Davis added 16 points. Mo Arnold had 10 points and six rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
